ActCanada Foundation for Sustainable Development Technology Act
PrecisAppointment of STEPHEN KUKUCHA of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a director of the Canada Foundation for Sustainable Development Technology, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, in the place of the Honourable Gary Lunn, P.C., whose term has expired.
